{"tid":1636501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港人唔係蠢既，係進步得慢。","createTime":"2019-10-07T18:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T18:21:27.000Z","uid":62011,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7db301caf139b7933f9640fc451824513063ad74","tid":1636501,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"好心痛啊，今晚好多手足/街坊被人拉，入嚟做個檢討。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1635905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1635905</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我開咗個POST問大家點解今晚咁多人被人拉。<br />\n<br />\n結論係將金鐘既陣地戰搬咗嚟18區，美其名18區開花。然後大家圍撚住某棟野係到嘈。18區陣地戰。<br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣唔會令班死差佬驚。更多的是好多無辜街坊手足被人拉。<br />\n<br />\n不如大家試下進步，陣地戰---&gt;流水戰術----&gt;空氣戰術。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家記唔記得，6月大埔連儂隧道有幅大型香蕉仔SIR既大頭相。嗰晚一貼，嚇到班狗轉登出防暴嚟撕相。其實班狗係怕自己資料畀曬街坊睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n六月以來，大家有老豆搵仔，點解唔同班死差佬玩黑色恐怖？ 將佢大頭相，個人資料周圍貼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><strong>快貼快走，唔好留低指紋，小心CCTV，小心臥底</strong></strong></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n你哋要好似遊魂野鬼亂咁走，亂咁貼。班差佬都會周圍跟住你哋，貼到邊佢哋撕到邊。"},{"pid":"b1108039e9adfcc5a1c39d1eee029c32c4d7f305","tid":1636501,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=wXQbzQ6sjjdDHWUhljjVf%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=243f59ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a> TWITTER戰線要人!!!, 每人出少少力已經幫到好多<br />\n<br />\n加油, 我地人多, 進化落去一定贏"},{"pid":"cf31dc7aeaaeaf83f629e74064b5429df380ef4f","tid":1636501,"uid":154040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:15:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蒙面冇罪<br />\n立法無理<br />\n全民口罩<br />\n以抗暴政</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbie4Of.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpbie4Of.png&h=4e2c4bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QD0APeV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQD0APeV.jpg&h=adc82dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vvJdGB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vvJdGB.jpg&h=21f72728&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0gqEwtg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0gqEwtg.jpg&h=f6ecf1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruOrbtg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FruOrbtg.jpg&h=bfae2022&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CsA1KOh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCsA1KOh.jpg&h=49059274&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0Z2ueX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0Z2ueX.jpg&h=cede51e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"017ed03a690ebcf94ef0f722484162fdc4030794","tid":1636501,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:21:27.000Z","msg":"無大台就係要從錯誤中學習"}]}